The Rams Head Group is a family owned and operated restaurant and entertainment company established in 1989 and based in Annapolis, Maryland. A ‘quintessential Key West’ bar and restaurant, formerly known as Blue Macaw, was purchased in 2019 and added to the Rams Head Group line-up as Rams Head Southernmost. Southernmost brings Rams Head’s love of craft beer and modern island fare in a casual atmosphere. Have a Question?
